              "pageContent": "Current UK Network\nProcess GuideConsiderationsRangeBatteryChargingServicingPHEVGlossary & Tools\nAt the end of July 2024, there were 66,779 charging points across \nthe UK, across 34,570 charging locations. This represents a 46% \nincrease in the number of public devices since July 2023.\n\n\nSource: Zap-Mapdatabase.Updated: August 2024\nHow many charging points are \nthere in the UK?\nZap-Stats – July 2024\n34,570\nLocations\n66,779\nDevices\n99,992\nConnectors\n2,004\nLast Month\nThis map shows all \npublic electric vehicle \nchargers in the UK as \nof July 2024.",
