              "pageContent": "We Charge Volkswagen offers you the fitting solution for charging your ID.4 in public when on the go. Remarkably simple to use via the We Connect ID. app, you can find available charging stations nearby, plan routes with automatic charging stop recommendations and automatically pay for your charging via your We Charge charging tariff\"},{\"kind\":\"disclaimer\",\"disclaimers\":\\[{\"displayType\":\"T4\\_ITEM\\_BASED\",\"text\":\"An offer from Volkswagen Group Charging GmbH (Elli).\",\"id\":\"DIS\\_134\",\"numericId\":\"DISN\\_145\"}\\]},{\"kind\":\"textNode\",\"value\":\" – including monthly billing and complete cost control. Throughout Europe you have access to approx. 150,000 charging points\"},{\"kind\":\"disclaimer\",\"disclaimers\":\\[{\"displayType\":\"T4\\_ITEM\\_BASED\",\"text\":\"More than 80% of the available European public charging infrastructure.\",\"id\":\"DIS\\_135\",\"numericId\":\"DISN\\_146\"}\\]},{\"kind\":\"textNode\",\"value\":\" including the whole IONITY quick charging network, which offers varying preferential terms depending on",
